snippet.title: Meet Junie: Your Autonomous Coding Partner in JetBrains IDEs
snippet.description:
Checkout Junie for JetBrains' IDEs: https://jb.gg/Junie-Engineer

Junie takes a completely different approach to coding assistance by planning, executing, and verifying each change instead of blindly generating code. In this video, I show how this workflow helps avoid the endless loop of bugs and fixes that most coding agents fall into.
